{"tid":2265170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地網民翻牆上維基 遭公安「定位」上門拉人 評論員：名副其實 「牆國」","createTime":"2020-10-31T08:12:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T10:23:53.000Z","uid":271829,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4c6d99df88217b9bf28293aba7b0cd6dff4f42ad","tid":2265170,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T08:12:03.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n根據公開資料，僅浙江一年內已處罰近70名「翻牆公民」。有內地律師批評當局允許官媒、外交部發言人、水軍翻牆到境外網站散佈消息，卻「只許州官放火，不許百姓點燈」。有時事評論員則指，在習近平治下的中國成為名副其實的「牆國」。<br />\n據自由亞洲電台報道，近日，有網民在社交媒體發佈浙江政務網一則對翻牆網民處罰的公告截圖，內容指網民張韜於「2019年上半年至2020年10月期間，透過百度搜索到翻牆軟件Lantern並下載，多次利用Lantern翻牆軟件非法訪問維基百科網站查詢資料」。上周六（24日），張韜在位於定海區環南街道名竹苑的建築內，被警方查獲及帶回偵訊。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201030/JYTELTLOTBBMNLZPJYHAXYN2DE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201030%2FJYTELTLOTBBMNLZPJYHAXYN2DE%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak8g1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=9c2e30d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201030%2FJYTELTLOTBBMNLZPJYHAXYN2DE%2F&h=6082db00\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201030/JYTELTLOTBBMNLZPJYHAXYN2DE/</a>"},{"pid":"4f49f8026e46759218fdb156164d11ce8ffc6236","tid":2265170,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T08:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定係查禁語先會拉尻佢"},{"pid":"5843d481f6823641bb430b3ff54341f63f484578","tid":2265170,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T08:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rEAJjgd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrEAJjgd.png&h=b6c785f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" c